        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Total production volume of hydraulic cement in Colombia in 2019: 12'900'000 ton. Source: USGS (2019). U.S. Geological Survey, Minerals Yearbook Annual Tables, 2019. Available at: &lt;https://www.usgs.gov/centers/national-minerals-information-center/cement-statistics-and-information&gt; 

